org.monetdb.embedded

Class MonetDBEmbedded

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.monetdb.embedded.MonetDBEmbedded

  • public class MonetDBEmbedded
extends Object
    Embedded version of MonetDB. Communication between Java and native C is done via JNI.
